{"tid":1853561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人間有愛 張記床上用品","createTime":"2020-01-31T04:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:52:49.000Z","uid":79916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0cacb502e943b48e14b5b1d11243e44f5d30a4","tid":1853561,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"1. 70蚊KLEAN MASK 50個 MFG:01.2020<br />\n2. 派麵包，派水比長面捱凍排隊等買口罩嘅市民<br />\n3. 老闆好友善安撫市民<br />\n<br />\n彩園邨嘅市民好感謝佢<br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎確診個案今日（30日）增至十宗，市民搶購口罩自保，市面「一罩難求」，有商舖藥房炒賣口罩，但同時亦有人派發口罩或良心價賣口罩，共度時艱。上水一間經營36年的床上用品小店，近日入口200盒泰國口罩，準備於周五（31日）以良心價發售，先到先得購買，少東指盼助市民度過難關，「香港咁樣，盡力幫吓手」，他批評「政府冇用，好多嘢唔應該市民做，應該政府幫市民做。」<br />\n<br />\nsource: hk01"},{"pid":"3c2a8dc402fe65ac021110959e25f4151b5448b3","tid":1853561,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:01:06.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"13a803594c70297cab09ab0642d64e34a553a23c","tid":1853561,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"天滅中共"},{"pid":"25a7bcd7521307f4a6d7f2da08ea06a3893e28f1","tid":1853561,"uid":79916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"全黨死清光"},{"pid":"6afa2a1f3057c398109bd06d68e60b9fee441ea6","tid":1853561,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"驅除共黨"},{"pid":"ed3ab5d7c2236afe9d242fbc5f1ef167362f39c1","tid":1853561,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\